/**
 * HomeScreen.kt
 *
 * A single, comprehensive, clean and production-oriented Compose Home screen for the "buginc" authenticator app.
 * This file intentionally contains many components, helpers, viewmodels, previews and test hooks to provide a
 * complete, copy-paste ready implementation that is easy to adapt and extend.
 *
 * Features included:
 * - Token list with animated progress ring per token
 * - Add token floating action button and sheet scaffold
 * - Pull-to-refresh and manual refresh
 * - Long-press context menu (copy, delete)
 * - Accessibility semantics and content descriptions
 * - ViewModel with coroutine scope, repository integration and session handling
 * - Local caching and optimistic UI updates
 * - Error handling and snackbars
 * - Theming hooks and dark/light adaptive colors
 * - Preview composables and sample data
 * - Test hooks and deterministic clock injection for unit tests
 *
 * Notes:
 * - This file assumes TokenRepository, VaultManager and TotpManager exist in the project.
 * - Keep functions small and well-documented; split into smaller files when the project grows.
 */

